<br>
You need 4 items for all 4 "basic" levels of the temple:<br>
<br>
1) Go to the basement level of the Shissar temple.<br>
<br>
2) Kill any of the named Taskmasters that can be used to trigger the Glyphed/Exiled/Cursed fights. The Taskmasters frequently drop the pouch necessary to combine the items.<br>
<br>
3) Once you have acquired the pouch. Head to the first floor and camp the random rare spawn Commander Zazuzh. He drops the idol you need.<br>
<br>
4) Once you've acquired the idol, go to the second floor and in similiar fashion camp the random rare spawn Commander Zeruzsh. He drops the ring you need.<br>
<br>
5) Then head to the Imperial Guard chamber where you can access the locked teleport to the Emperor's chamber. By killing the Imperial Guards you can spawn 3 named rares all of which drop the last piece you need, the insignia. These are General Kizuhx, Arbiter Korazhk, and Advisor Zekuzh.<br>
<br>
6) Put all 3 items into the pouch and combine. You will receive a Ring of the Shissar.<br>
<br>
<br>
